{"tid":1893305,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[減肥sharing] 我3個月減左12磅","createTime":"2020-02-23T07:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T15:44:03.000Z","uid":295872,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3751f7447cb55ad381c8a5a230cf2122b47071","tid":1893305,"uid":295872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"見咁多人講減肥post 我又分享下經歷先。有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfgPQGV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfgPQGV.png&h=1b48972f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身都已經唔係瘦底，再加埋之前做sales 成日要飲飲食食，成個人漲到好似剛剛生完仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛剛有朋友介紹話每個月$850減肥，咁我就把心一橫試佢一試，諗住就算唔得都唔會太肉赤。終於由128磅減到去116磅，本身我想減到去110磅，但營養師話我BMI 計會過瘦，所以去到116就完成個減磅program。<br />\n<br />\n我個營養師完全唔洗見面，全程用whatsapp 溝通，方便我唔洗就時間見佢。一星期兩次要同佢報告身體狀況同埋食左啲咩。因為做sales 要見客關係，有時都好難唔飲飲食食，再加上我個時又腰痛又腳痛，我除左一星期放一次狗之前都無運動。有時一星期一餐大魚大肉，但之後要捱番兩日地獄餐。成過過程都算叫飽既，因為可以無限量食菜。中間無運動，咁樣3個月後就減咁12磅啦。<br />\n<br />\n我都減完肥三年，而家都仲keep 到116，咁講真我自己覺得我飲食習慣都改變咗，但我都會食麻辣邊爐同勁多芝士嘅野，只係食完之後自已balance 番囉。我而家見番我自己啲舊相都覺得得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bc729d65430003073f0d961f757813d936061a","tid":1893305,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"肥啲好似有肉地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850ec3317008709cb0b77d902cfb850604ae4cf6","tid":1893305,"uid":299794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"賣廣告定咩"},{"pid":"850cbfffcc300904fa972dade055143c41a759c2","tid":1893305,"uid":60435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"850ec3317008709cb0b77d902cfb850604ae4cf6","tid":1893305,"uid":299794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"賣廣告定咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:18:17.000Z","msg":"明顯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f1dc0b21f9a555a33a1d832800e9cb3759dcf3","tid":1893305,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp營養師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我係WhatsApp健身教練"},{"pid":"e11593f2b8151dc22a9d60d0eec0c7c908ab9151","tid":1893305,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55f1dc0b21f9a555a33a1d832800e9cb3759dcf3","tid":1893305,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp營養師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我係WhatsApp健身教練"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係WhatsApp侍應"},{"pid":"f9018ab66b1c9c094a1fb321438c14d76d0867a2","tid":1893305,"uid":182712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓主真樣"},{"pid":"eb8b6ecf793aed113eff45605ae48f8c89bb146d","tid":1893305,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"弱智<br />\n洗撚營養師咩<br />\n我教你都得啦"}]}